								StaticText '100%'
						StaticText 'The customer service was outstanding- The website was a little jumpy and I was wish-washy on sizing and somehow ended up ordering 2 of the same size- Emma sent an email @ 8:00 Saturday morning and immediately corrected and confirmed my order - it arrived earlier than the given date- Good work w/ attention to detail!The shirt looks great- Bright green didn’t fade and lettering remained intact ( washed cold- dried low for 5 minutes/ then line-dried)It fit as indicated- very good & accurate sizing chart- I should have ordered a size up though to get the oversized look- didn’t think that thru!The weight is tee- shirt rather than a true jersey- so light weight-Overall - love the shirt and the customer service -Would order again from this company!'
